object.customQuery:
select
	distinct 
q.cmm_container as underwriting_question_and_answer_type,
	q.id as underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key,
	q.system_id as source_system_system_id,
	q.id as source_system_id,
	q.parent_id as source_system_parent_id,
	q.name as underwriting_question_code,
	q.value as underwriting_answer,
	q.visible_ind as question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator ,
	q.text as text,
	q.display_desc as display_description,
	q.row_id as source_system_row_id,
	prkr.line_of_business,
	case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.parent_child_indicator
		else null 
	end as parent_or_child_indicator,
	case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then pq.question
		else NULL
	end as parent_question_code_of_child_question,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then pr.value
		else NULL
	end as parent_answer_of_child_question,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.priority_order
		else NULL
	end as question_and_answer_hierarchy,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.display_when_reply_is_no_or_null
		else NULL
	end as display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null
		else NULL
	end as display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null
		else NULL
	end as display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
		case
		when prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners' then qrpcr.display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null
		else NULL
	end as display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null,
	tgt.underwriting_question_and_answer_id,
	tgt.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_md5checksum
from
	bronze.acx_question_reply q
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
on
	q.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
	and q.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join bronze.question_reply_parent_child_reference_for_homeowners qrpcr
on
	q.name = qrpcr.question
left join bronze.question_reply_parent_child_reference_for_homeowners pq
on qrpcr.parent_question_id_of_child = pq.question_id
AND pq.question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_row_effective_end_datetime  = '9999-12-31'
left join bronze.acx_question_reply pr
on q.system_id = pr.system_id 
and q.cmm_container = pr.cmm_container 
and pq.question = pr.name
AND pr.acx_question_reply_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
left join silver.underwriting_questions_and_answers tgt 
on q.system_id = tgt.source_system_system_id 
and q.cmm_container = tgt.underwriting_question_and_answer_type 
and q.id = tgt.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key 
and tgt.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where
	 prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
	and qrpcr.question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
    and q.acx_question_reply_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
AND q.acx_question_reply_row_effective_start_datetime >= '2025-07-01';

fields.name: v_record_display_indicator_decode
fields.expression:

ISNULL(underwriting_answer),display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
underwriting_answer = 'No', display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
underwriting_answer = 'NO',display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
underwriting_answer = 'N', display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
underwriting_answer = 'Yes', display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
underwriting_answer = 'YES', display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
underwriting_answer = 'Y', display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null)

fields.name: v_parent_display_indicator_decode
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
ISNULL(parent_answer_of_child_question), display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'No', display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'NO', display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'N', display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'YES', display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'Yes', display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
parent_answer_of_child_question = 'Y', display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null,
display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null)

fields.name: src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5(
'underwriting_question_and_answer_type' || underwriting_question_and_answer_type ||
'underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key' || underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key ||
'source_system_system_id' || to_char(source_system_system_id) ||
'source_system_id' || to_char(source_system_id) ||
'source_system_parent_id' || source_system_parent_id ||
'underwriting_question_code' || underwriting_question_code ||
'underwriting_answer' || underwriting_answer ||
'question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator' || question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator ||
'text' || text ||
'display_description' || display_description ||
'source_system_row_id' || to_char(source_system_row_id) ||
'parent_or_child_indicator' || parent_or_child_indicator ||
'parent_question_code_of_child_question' || parent_question_code_of_child_question ||
'question_and_answer_hierarchy' || to_char(question_and_answer_hierarchy) ||
'display_when_reply_is_no_or_null' || display_when_reply_is_no_or_null ||
'display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null' || display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null ||
'display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null' || display_when_parent_reply_is_yes_or_not_null ||
'display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null' || display_when_parent_reply_is_no_or_null ||
'line_of_business' || line_of_business
)
